metadata.name: Bumblebees and Flowers
metadata.description:
Cross embroidery by Elyna. 
Handmade. 202 hours spent.
Cotton canvas 40 x 30 cm (15¾'' x 11¾'').
39 colors.

''This embroidery will perfectly complement the interior as a picture. A lot of effort and soul was invested in this embroidery. I love her!'' — Elyna.
